name: Golf Wolf - Trick Shot
description: Wolves are very determined creatures.. Even when it comes to golf! That's why in this game to pass the level you must make a all of the shots on each level. You will get 10 golf balls per level to us to pass. Beware though, once you reach 1 you will lose, not 0! Do you have what it takes to pass all of the levels? try now for free!
